<h3>2 Week Boot Camp Agreement</h3>
<p>
  I {{{registration.name.full}}}, agree to the following terms and conditions.  
</p>


<p>
  I will be expected to attend at least <strong>9 of the 10 boot camp classes</strong> (within the 2 week boot camp) in order to be eligible for full membership in the SEAL Team Physical Training Program. 
</p>

<p>If I purchase a 2 week boot camp membership at a professional or student discount, I understand I may be asked to show documents which demonstrate the fact that I am either a member of the US Military, a first responder or a full-time student.
  </p>

