</p>

<p>
  SEAL Team Physical Training reserves the right from time to time to establish general policies that apply to all fitness program members regarding attendance, conduct, safety, contract cancellation and other relevant subjects, and to modify these polices.  Any such policies will be posted on SEAL Team Physical Training web site or sent out via E-mail.
</p>

